narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: What goes in the prospectus (archive, question, method, etc.) this was very helpful and has helped me shape the project. Feedback on presentation also.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Strengths: presentation practice for the lightning talks. Weaknesses: None really. For future instances it could be productive to have students prepare a first draft and discuss it in the seminar. That way every student goes into the Winter holidays with a first draft of the prospectus. This would perhaps mean having the Lightning Talks on the (two) Friday(s) before Thanksgiving break. I think that should be feasible.
